    <h2> Advantages of owning your own car </h2>
    <ul>
        <li> You don't depend on public transport schedules </li>
        <li> If you suddenly want to go somewhere at an untimely time (for example, at night), you do not need to order a taxi </li>
        <li> You feel the freedom of movement </li>
        <li> In the rain, blizzard, cold and extreme heat, it is much more pleasant to drive your car than to wait for transport at the bus stop </li>
    </ul>
